pull_request.title: Don't rely on bashism in Makefile
pull_request.body:
`/bin/sh` doesn't necessarily understand `[[`. 

```
root@18a2f0f4f26e:/# /bin/sh
# [[
/bin/sh: 1: [[: not found
```
